==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Esloin
<hw>Es*loin"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Eloign</er>.]</ety> <def>To remove; to banish; to withdraw; to
avoid; to eloign.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From worldly cares he did himself <qex>esloin</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Esnecy</ent>⟦br⟧
